{"tid":865671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂用中國死囚做標本 「真實人體展」遭瑞士洛桑封殺","createTime":"2018-10-17T08:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T23:54:15.000Z","uid":11148,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"71178bfbfe132010591695a664ad7bee5a6df098","tid":865671,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181017/58803189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58803189&d=Z1qCflbjvdOU9%2BWWpJONNnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=37c98264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58803189&h=46ba72c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181017/58803189</a><br />\n瑞士洛桑當局周二禁止一個人體標本展覽舉行，擔心標本是來自受酷刑致死或被處決的中國囚犯。<br />\n當局接到「基督徒廢除酷刑行動」組織（ACAT）投訴後，勒令原定周五起一連三天舉行的「真實人體展」（Real Human Bodies）取消。ACAT指所展出的塑化人體標本，很可能是中國死囚或法輪功成員。伯爾尼當局要求展覽主辦單位提供標本的來源保證，以及死者或其親屬的同意書，否則禁示展覽會舉行。<br />\n展覽負責人胡佩茨（Hubert Huppertz）向當地一份報章聲稱，持有相關文件。<br />\n「真實人體展」<span style=\"color: red;\">展示有骨肉有器官的塑化人體標本</span>，先後在荷蘭、比利時和瑞士首都伯爾尼舉行，ACAT瑞士支部曾試圖阻止伯爾尼展覽失敗。德國解剖學家哈根斯（Gunter von Hagens）的「人體奧妙展」（Body Worlds）去年在日內瓦舉行時，亦一度引起爭議。2002年本港亦曾有類似的人體奧妙展展覽，主辦方及展品來自日本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181017/large/1539748706_9e9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181017%2Flarge%2F1539748706_9e9e.jpg&h=d72b9efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.goodsmile.info/cgm/images/product/20140821/4553/30061/large/916f8fbad7d1b348d4294abe9e0130b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.goodsmile.info%2Fcgm%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2F20140821%2F4553%2F30061%2Flarge%2F916f8fbad7d1b348d4294abe9e0130b3.jpg&h=6aeeae14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />